{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had money because after, after the clinic was bombed out, we got a commendation for by the-- by the government fellow amount that was pretty much equal in the income that we had, of the clinic had.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was part of the-- oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The money wasn't worth anything, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't do-- everything was rationed, goods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you still needed money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you couldn't buy anything extraordinary, any luxury, you just had your bare-- food was all-- was, you know, severely rationed, clothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had money, so we got-- went to Silesia and with those friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I immediately signed up the-- filled out the forms at the local police department in that community.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a few days later, I got a summons to report to work to a big factory that was making-- refurbishing big steam rollers, putting a rubber-- a layer of rubber-- levels of rubber on these steam rollers, which were then used in other factories to make clothes out of wood.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was actually-- an actual-- an actual like way that they made-- that the German army made uniforms for their people, out of wood, because they had no wool.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germany was totally cut off by the Naval blockade by all the Allied troops, so wool-- there wasn't very much wool production in Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they needed uniforms, so they made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a liquid, and made it into a liquid mass, the wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they would somehow, through a chemicals process, they would convert this into, into fabrics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very stiff, and I think people scratched a lot, but, [LAUGHS] but that was all right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, we were-- the factory wasn't making those uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were making the tools for it, those big steamrollers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
